    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for this absolute gem. It\u2019s been super reliable and is still looking great inside and out\u2014perfect for someone who wants a solid, stylish ride without the brand-new price tag. It drives like a dream and has been so well-loved! You\u2019re going to have a blast behind the wheel. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
