    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and daily utility. The exterior paint retains a brilliant luster, showing only the minor, incidental stone chips consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin is a testament to pride of ownership; the premium upholstery is free of stains or significant bolsters wear, and the interior has never been smoked in. Every electronic component, from the responsive infotainment screen to the heated seats and climate control, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health, benefiting from a documented history of timely oil changes and preventative maintenance. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains tight and quiet over bumps. With a fresh set of tires and recent brake service, this car is ready for immediate delivery and many miles of worry-free driving. It comes with both sets of keys and all original owner manuals.",
      "price": 34800.0,
